text: Break in the Circle is a 1955 British drama movie directed by Val Guest and starring Forrest Tucker, Eva Bartok, Marius Goring, Guy Middleton, Eric Pohlmann, Reginald Beckwith. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1955 drama movies Category:British drama movies Category:Movies directed by Val Guest
